net.metarelate.terminology.config
Class CoreConfig

java.lang.Object
  net.metarelate.terminology.config.CoreConfig

public class CoreConfig
extends java.lang.Object

Provide static strings used within the system (they are not meant to be used in the RDF representation of terminologies) Also allows the redfinition of some system properties.

Author:
andrea_splendiani
